"Complain about a United States Embassy or Consulate","Learn how to complain about an embassy or consulate.","<p>To complain about waste, fraud, abuse, mismanagement, or misconduct at a <a href=""http://www.usembassy.gov/"">U.S. embassy or consulate</a>, first try to resolve the issue with that embassy or consulate.</p><br />
<p>If you are unable to do so for any reason, learn <a href=""http://oig.state.gov/hotline/"">how to file a complaint</a> with the <a href=""http://oig.state.gov/"">Office of Inspector General (OIG)</a> in the U.S. Department of State (DOS).</p><br />
