</ul><p>For more information about federal tax resources, contact the <a href=""http://www.irs.gov/uac/How-to-Contact-the-IRS-1"">Internal Revenue Service</a>. You can also contact your <a href=""http://www.taxadmin.org/fta/link/default.php?lnk=10#"">state's tax department</a> for information that is specific to your state.</p><br />
