"Lowering the Cost of College","If you are looking to lower your cost for college, this page offers several options.","<p>If you are looking to lower your costs for college, these resources may be helpful:</p><br />
<p><a href=""https://studentaid.ed.gov/repay-loans/understand/plans/income-driven"">Income-Based Repayment (IBR)</a><br /><a href=""https://studentaid.ed.gov/repay-loans/forgiveness-cancellation/charts/public-service"">Public Service Loan Forgiveness (PSLF)</a><br /><a href=""http://www2.ed.gov/programs/fws/index.html"">Federal Work-Study Program</a></p><br />
<p>Check with your school or <a href=""http://www2.ed.gov/about/contacts/state/index.html"">state department of education</a> to see if they offer loan relief or reduction programs in exchange for your service in a specific field of study for a certain period of time.</p><br />
