"Get Copies and Transcripts of Your Tax Returns","Learn how to get copies and transcripts of your tax returns and supporting documentation.","<p>Do you need a copy of your <a href=""http://www.irs.gov/taxtopics/tc156.html"">prior year tax return</a>? If you need an exact copy of a previously filed tax return and attachements, you can get it by mailing the following items:</p><br />
