"Manage and Waste","Learn about waste management, waste disposal and reducing waste. ","<p>Each year, we generate tons of waste in our homes, businesses and communities. The EPA is challenging all citizens to conserve our natural resources by committing to reduce, reuse, and recycle.</p><br />
<p>Reduce and reuse by buying used or reusable items over disposable; look for products with less packaging; maintain and repair products instead of buying new; and borrow, rent or share items that are used infrequently.  Learn how you can <a href=""http://www2.epa.gov/recycle"">reduce waste</a>.</p><br />
