"Water Quality","Find out about the water quality of the drinking and ground water in your area. and report any problems.","<p>Water quality is determined by the presence and quantity of contaminants, and varies depending on where you live. General information about <a href=""http://www.usgs.gov/water/"">surface and ground water quality</a>, as well as <a href=""http://water.epa.gov/drink/"">ground and drinking water</a> is available.</p><br />
