<li><strong>Non-Emergencies:</strong> To report adverse reactions or other problems with bottled water, contact your <a href=""http://www.fda.gov/Safety/ReportaProblem/ConsumerComplaintCoordinators/"">local FDA Consumer Complaint Coordinator</a>.</li><br />
</ul></li><br />
