<li><a href=""http://apps.americanbar.org/legalservices/lris/directory/"">Online Lawyer Referral Directory</a></li><br />
<li><a href=""http://statesidelegal.org/"">Stateside Legal</a> - Free legal help for military members, veterans, and their families</li><br />
