"Fishing","Learn about laws and regulations when fishing in recreational areas.","<p>Laws and regulations managing recreational fishing vary greatly. These commonly include:</p><br />
<ul><li>Permits (licenses)</li><br />
<li>Closed periods (seasons) where specific species are unavailable for harvest</li><br />
<li>Restrictions on gear types</li><br />
<li>Quotas</li><br />
