<li><a href=""http://www.senate.gov/reference/common/faq/retirement_for_members.shtml"">Congressional Pensions</a></li><br />
</ul><p>For more information about Congressional salaries and benefits, contact the <a href=""http://www.usa.gov/directory/federal/senate.shtml"">U.S. Senate</a> and/or the <a href=""http://www.usa.gov/directory/federal/house-of-representatives.shtml"">U.S. House of Representatives</a>.</p><br />
