"Benefit Programs for Federal Employees and Survivors","Information on benefits programs available to federal employees and survivors.","<p>For information on and help with federal benefits, contact your agency's personnel/human resources office or call the <a href=""http://www.usa.gov/directory/federal/office-of-personnel-management.shtml"">Office of Personnel Management (OPM)</a>.</p><br />
