"Establish Citizenship Without a Birth Certificate","How to get documents that can help prove your U.S. citizenship. ","<p>If you were born in the U.S. and there is no birth certificate on file, you will need several different documents to prove your citizenship:</p><br />
<ul><li>A letter from the <a href=""http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/w2w.htm"">vital records office in your birth state</a> with your name and what years they searched for your birth certificate.</li><br />
