"Adoption and Foster Care","Information on adoption and foster care resources","<p>Browse the <a href=""https://www.childwelfare.gov/nfcad/"">National Foster Care and Adoption Directory</a> to view adoption and foster care resources by state. You may also search the directory using keywords.</p><br />
