<li>Census population data is used to divide <a href=""http://www.census.gov/population/apportionment/"">the seats in the U.S. House of Representatives</a> among the 50 states.</li><br />
<li>Curious about whether a request you received to participate in a U.S. Census Bureau survey is real?<br />
