"Internet Fraud","How to report Internet fraud.","<p>The term ""Internet fraud"" generally refers to any type of fraud scheme that uses online services, such as chat rooms, e-mail, message boards, or websites, to:</p><br />
<ul><li>Solicit prospective victims.</li><br />
<li>Make fraudulent transactions.</li><br />
<li>Transmit the proceeds of fraud to financial institutions or others connected with the scheme.</li><br />
